ADD IN THE STYLE TAG



.alert {
  padding: 20px;
  background-color: #f44336;
  color: white;
}

.closebtn {
  margin-left: 15px;
  color: white;
  font-weight: bold;
  float: right;
  font-size: 22px;
  line-height: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.closebtn:hover {
  color: black;
}
</style>



<div class="alert">
  <span class="closebtn" onclick="this.parentElement.style.display='none';">&times;</span> 
   <h4><center><strong>Announcement:</strong> Products shop now open!  <a href="https://www.bonfire.com/store/fairserve/">Click here to see our awesome new products!</a> </center>
</div>